L's Dark Art Collection
# 1 ~ Omen ~

The Dark Art Collection is a mysterious work with Gothic movies and horror tastes with forests and scenes as motifs.
We will continue to increase the number of works in the future.
It is finished in a painting style based on the photograph, and combines animation composition and sound.
Please add a dark piece to your collection.
